\newlabel{tab:lemon}{{2}{9}{Experiment 2 (The Lemon Market) --- Deceptive revenue share, buyer welfare, market collapse timestep, and Sybil detection rate ($T=30$ steps, $K=5$ Sybil cluster; mean $\pm $ std over 10 episodes)}{table.2}{}}
