\newlabel{fig:lemon_volume}{{4}{10}{Experiment 2 (The Lemon Market) --- Trading volume $V_t$ (left axis) and average seller reputation $\bar {R}_t$ (right axis) over 30 timesteps for base vs.\ Skeptical Guardian buyers. Vertical marker at $t=15$ indicates the ``Flood of Fakes'' shock (Experiment 3). Guardian buyers arrest reputation collapse and sustain market volume}{figure.4}{}}
